column9: Ok, city trans is making money by flying passengers across the map, when they are only going nextdoor?  Is this fair play?  If so, I will be doing the same
Also, this is why all our other routes are one sided, the capacity of this is so low, all my (and abi) routes run to teh exchange full, but leave empty, bc there is nowhere near enought capacity
